                "invention-title": [
                    "Magnetic regulation and control catalyst, preparation method thereof and ammonia-hydrogen energy catalytic conversion application of magnetic regulation and control catalyst",
                    "磁性调控催化剂、其制备方法及其氨-氢能源催化转化应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a magnetic regulation and control catalyst and a preparation method and ammonia-hydrogen energy catalytic conversion application thereof, and belongs to the technical field of ammonia synthesis and decomposition, and the magnetic regulation and control catalyst comprises a magnetic component and an electron spin regulation and control component; the magnetic component is a main magnetic component and/or an auxiliary magnetic component; the main magnetic component is one or a combination of two or more of iron oxides; the auxiliary magnetic component is one or a combination of two or more of nickel oxide and cobalt oxide; and the electron spin regulation and control component is one or a combination of two or more of scandium oxide, yttrium oxide and lanthanide oxides. According to the present invention, the electron spin regulation and control component as the electron transfer intermediate is added to the magnetic regulation and control catalyst to regulate and control the electron spin state and the magnetic moment of the main magnetic component and the auxiliary magnetic component, such that the catalyst has strong N2 activation performance under the rapid regulation of the electromagnetic field so as to significantly reduce the activation energy of N2, therefore, the ammonia synthesis efficiency is improved at low temperature and low pressure."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了磁性调控催化剂、其制备方法及其氨‑氢能源催化转化应用，属于氨合成与分解技术领域，包括磁性成分与电子自旋调控成分；磁性成分为主磁成分和/或副磁成分；主磁成分为铁的氧化物中一种或两种及以上组合；副磁成分为镍的氧化物、钴的氧化物中的一种或两种及以上组合；电子自旋调控成分为氧化钪、氧化钇、镧系氧化物中的一种或两种及以上组合。在磁性调控催化剂中加入作为电子转移中间体的电子自旋调控成分，对主磁成分和副磁成分的电子自旋态和磁矩进行调控，使得催化剂在电磁场的快速调节下具有更强的N2活化性能，进而显著降低N2的活化能，从而在低温低压下提升氨合成效率。"
                }
            ]
        }
